# Liver Transplant Data Analysis

## Overview
This project analyzes liver transplant waitlist data to identify patterns, disparities, and key factors affecting patient outcomes.

## Objectives
- Data cleaning and preprocessing
- Exploratory data analysis (EDA)
- Identify racial and demographic disparities
- Analyze transplant waitlist trends over time
- Generate actionable healthcare insights

## Tools & Technologies
- Python (Pandas, NumPy)
- Matplotlib / Seaborn
- Jupyter Notebook
- Statistical Analysis

## Key Analyses
- Missing value handling
- Distribution of patient demographics
- Waitlist trend analysis
- Racial disparity investigation
- Correlation analysis between variables

## Key Findings (example)
- Significant variation in waitlist times across demographic groups
- Regional disparities in transplant access
- Strong correlation between certain clinical variables and waitlist outcomes

## Output
- Cleaned dataset
- EDA notebooks
- Visualizations and insights

